Class BurnoutTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team1540.rooster.testers.AbstractTester<ChickenTalon,Boolean>
      • org.team1540.rooster.testers.BurnoutTester
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sendable, Runnable, Tester<ChickenTalon,Boolean>

    public class BurnoutTester
extends AbstractTester<ChickenTalon,Boolean>
implements Sendable
    Reports motor burnouts by comparing the current draw across a series of similarly-purposed motors and reporting low outliers.
